description:
&lt;p&gt;We are delighted to be offering an exciting new opportunity for a Clinical Lead Speech and Language Therapist to join our AMH teams across Durham and Darlington. They will offer speech, language, communication and eating and drinking assessment and intervention to working age adults with mental ill health&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful applicant will work across inpatient and community services in Durham &amp; Darlington to provide professional and clinical leadership on behalf of SLT within those areas. The Clinical Lead will also be an integral part of the senior leadership group within our services and will be required to attend clinical governance meetings in respect of this.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful applicant will be able to demonstrate excellent communication and interpersonal skills and be able to articulate the value of Speech and Language Therapy for AMH services.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Robust supervision arrangements and joint development review will facilitate opportunities for continuing professional development.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Hannah Crawford - Professional Head of Speech &amp; Language Therapy - 07775 031046 hannahcrawford@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
